{"tha-ap438:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap438:0.2":"Ekaviharivagga ","tha-ap438:0.3":"6 Kalambadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap438:1.1":"“Romaso nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap438:1.2":"vasate pabbatantare; ","tha-ap438:1.3":"Kalambam tassa padasim, ","tha-ap438:1.4":"pasanno sehi panibhi. ","tha-ap438:2.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap438:2.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap438:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap438:2.4":"kalambassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap438:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap438:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap438:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap438:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap438:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap438:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap438:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap438:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap438:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap438:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kalambadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap438:7.1":"Kalambadayakattherassapadanam chattham. "}